      "span_text": "As it was mentioned, in the course of this chapter there are presented only selected, general results obtained during solving the Zitzler-Deb-Thiele test suite which in the literature is known and identified as the set of test problems ZDT1-ZDT6 ( (Zitzler, 1999, p. 57-63),, (Deb, 2001, p. 356-362), (Coello et al., 2007, p. 194-199) )."
